

1. Download/Prep

    A.)
        sudo su
        mkdir -p /var/azuracast
        cd /var/azuracast
    B.)
        curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AzuraCast/AzuraCast/main/docker.sh > docker.sh
        chmod a+x docker.sh
        ./docker.sh install

the docker.sh file will do everything you need.

2. docker-compose up --build
    - docker-compose down

